<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        h1 { color: #ffc107; } /* Orange/Yellow */
        p { line-height: 1.6; }
        .details-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 20px; }
        .details-table th, .details-table td { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px; text-align: left; }
        .details-table th { background-color: #f2f2f2; }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ffc107;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #777; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Withdrawal Approved!</h1>
        <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
        <p>Your withdrawal request for <strong>${{amount}}</strong> has been successfully approved!</p>

        <table class="details-table">
            <tr>
                <th>Amount</th>
                <td>${{amount}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Payment Method</th>
                <td>{{paymentMethod}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Status</th>
                <td>{{status}}</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <p>The funds are now being processed and should arrive in provided payment details shortly, typically within 1-3 business days.</p>
        <p>Thank you for your patience!</p>
        <p>Regards,<br>Your Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        This is an automated email. Please do not reply.
    </div>
</body>
</html>
